[Anfu Hall]

5
00:00:49,030 --> 00:00:49,710
Father.

6
00:00:51,470 --> 00:00:51,920
Father.

7
00:01:01,430 --> 00:01:01,840
You.

8
00:01:02,470 --> 00:01:03,520
You're a devil.

9
00:01:04,320 --> 00:01:05,960
I'm going to kill you.

10
00:01:09,320 --> 00:01:10,440
[One year later]

11
00:01:10,600 --> 00:01:11,800
The daughter of the Prime Minister,

12
00:01:11,980 --> 00:01:14,500
Xu Qingqing,
is gentle, virtuous, and elegant.

13
00:01:15,080 --> 00:01:19,120
I bestow her to
Northern General Gu Shenghan.

14
00:01:19,560 --> 00:01:21,440
Choose an auspicious day

15
00:01:21,440 --> 00:01:23,160
[Prime Minister's Daughter, Xu Qingqing]
and proceed with the wedding promptly.

16
00:01:23,160 --> 00:01:24,400
[Prime Minister's Daughter, Xu Qingqing]

17
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:26,330
Rather than marrying

18
00:01:26,350 --> 00:01:28,910
a bloodthirsty cripple
with a decadent mind,

19
00:01:31,410 --> 00:01:33,130
I would rather die.

20
00:01:33,870 --> 00:01:35,960
You cannot bring yourself to seek death.

21
00:01:36,450 --> 00:01:38,070
[Xu Liulang's daughter, Xu Yin]

22
00:01:42,010 --> 00:01:43,490
To seek death recklessly

23
00:01:43,950 --> 00:01:45,240
is to defy the imperial decree.

24
00:01:45,550 --> 00:01:47,930
Disgrace will fall upon
the Prime Minister's Manor.

25
00:01:48,070 --> 00:01:49,770
And the one who benefits the most

26
00:01:49,890 --> 00:01:51,110
will be Gu Shenghan.

27
00:01:51,310 --> 00:01:52,810
You talk too much.

28
00:01:53,930 --> 00:01:55,450
I'll seal that mouth of yours.

29
00:01:55,690 --> 00:01:57,710
Rather than killing yourself in vain,

30
00:01:58,190 --> 00:01:59,470
why don't you kill him instead?

31
00:02:03,610 --> 00:02:05,250
I would like to know what great plans

32
00:02:05,310 --> 00:02:06,810
a servant like you can come up with.

33
00:02:09,850 --> 00:02:12,350
I'm willing to marry
Gu Shenghan on your behalf

34
00:02:12,630 --> 00:02:13,990
and kill him.

35
00:02:16,690 --> 00:02:19,990
It's said that he's now a cannibal.

36
00:02:21,190 --> 00:02:22,590
Aren't you afraid?

37
00:02:23,550 --> 00:02:25,050
My feud with him for killing my father

38
00:02:25,410 --> 00:02:27,090
is irreconcilable.

39
00:02:32,470 --> 00:02:34,170
How unexpected.

40
00:02:34,970 --> 00:02:37,070
There are countless people

41
00:02:37,490 --> 00:02:39,610
who want to kill Gu Shenghan.

42
00:02:44,570 --> 00:02:47,370
Our appearances are vastly different.

43
00:02:48,030 --> 00:02:49,610
How can you marry him on my behalf?

44
00:02:50,290 --> 00:02:53,050
I have a method
to flawlessly imitate your appearance.

45
00:02:55,590 --> 00:02:57,790
With this powder,
I can replicate someone's appearance.

46
00:02:58,170 --> 00:02:59,050
There won't be any difference.

47
00:03:00,110 --> 00:03:01,990
However, intense pain
comes with the use of this powder.

48
00:03:02,310 --> 00:03:03,670
An ordinary person can't bear this.

49
00:03:12,110 --> 00:03:13,090
Gu Shenghan.

50
00:03:13,870 --> 00:03:15,390
Tomorrow is your death day.

51
00:03:16,390 --> 00:03:18,100
[Northern General's Manor]
General, spare me.

52
00:03:18,380 --> 00:03:18,900
General.

53
00:03:24,870 --> 00:03:27,350
[Northern General, Gu Shenghan]
Since the marriage bestowed by the Emperor,

54
00:03:27,430 --> 00:03:28,990
Xu Qingqing has been
threatening to kill herself in protest.

55
00:03:29,030 --> 00:03:30,610
Yesterday, she even
got drunk at the Zuixian Restaurant

56
00:03:30,670 --> 00:03:31,710
and publicly insulted you.

57
00:03:31,990 --> 00:03:33,750
Should I send someone to bring her here?

58
00:03:34,550 --> 00:03:35,470
It's unnecessary.

59
00:03:36,350 --> 00:03:39,250
But the wedding is
on the day of the full moon.

60
00:03:39,870 --> 00:03:41,150
I'm worried about you, General.

61
00:03:41,870 --> 00:03:43,430
The Prime Minister
holds great power now,

62
00:03:43,470 --> 00:03:44,450
and the royal authority is diminishing.

63
00:03:44,970 --> 00:03:46,590
Only my Northern Garrison

64
00:03:46,650 --> 00:03:48,230
can stand on equal ground with them.

65
00:03:48,530 --> 00:03:49,690
This marriage alliance

66
00:03:50,290 --> 00:03:52,570
is nothing more than seeing a battle

67
00:03:52,610 --> 00:03:53,970
between me and Xu Guoru.

68
00:03:57,550 --> 00:03:59,950
I'll give them a satisfactory wedding.

69
00:04:01,110 --> 00:04:02,990
[Prime Minister's Manor]

70
00:04:11,510 --> 00:04:13,250
I heard that
she's adopted by the Prime Minister.

71
00:04:13,330 --> 00:04:14,190
Really?

72
00:04:14,270 --> 00:04:15,470
No wonder
the Prime Minister is not heartbroken

73
00:04:15,910 --> 00:04:16,690
that she's marrying

74
00:04:16,710 --> 00:04:18,470
the crippled General who is a cannibal.

75
00:04:18,970 --> 00:04:20,550
Let's hope she remain safe and sound.

76
00:04:21,890 --> 00:04:24,530
♪Disturbing a dream♪

77
00:04:26,250 --> 00:04:28,270
♪Once merely a speck of cosmic dust♪

78
00:04:28,890 --> 00:04:31,330
♪Ensnared in folly's fervent lust♪

79
00:04:33,250 --> 00:04:35,250
♪If life's illusions♪

80
00:04:37,250 --> 00:04:38,990
♪Were encased
within the circles of time♪

81
00:04:39,350 --> 00:04:41,610
♪Lingering desires awaken anew♪

82
00:04:42,250 --> 00:04:44,410
♪With a fervent kiss♪

83
00:04:44,470 --> 00:04:45,630
[Happy Wedding]

84
00:04:47,290 --> 00:04:49,510
♪The withered grass leaves no trace♪

85
00:04:50,170 --> 00:04:52,310
♪Buried a lifetime♪

86
00:04:52,370 --> 00:04:53,850
[Harmonious Climate]

87
00:04:54,690 --> 00:04:56,690
♪The unresolved hatred♪

88
00:04:57,370 --> 00:04:59,370
♪Carved another inch into the bone♪

89
00:05:01,950 --> 00:05:04,170
♪If there were never deep feelings♪

90
00:05:05,450 --> 00:05:07,110
♪Knocking on the door of my heart♪

91
00:05:07,870 --> 00:05:10,010
♪Missed in a fleeting glance♪

92
00:05:10,410 --> 00:05:13,450
♪The original person♪

93
00:05:14,250 --> 00:05:17,690
♪Thoughts of you entered my dreams♪

94
00:05:18,210 --> 00:05:20,870
♪No one to share the same pillow♪

95
00:05:20,930 --> 00:05:22,500
The auspicious time has come.

96
00:05:22,950 --> 00:05:24,970
A bow to the heaven and earth.

97
00:05:25,930 --> 00:05:28,380
For eternity.

98
00:05:28,590 --> 00:05:31,170
♪I endured
a century of snowstorm in vain♪

99
00:05:31,370 --> 00:05:32,330
Shenghan.

100
00:05:32,870 --> 00:05:34,110
The ceremony is not yet complete.

101
00:05:37,290 --> 00:05:39,130
Old Madam is
a Buddhist and a simple person.

102
00:05:39,170 --> 00:05:40,770
So, the ceremony
should be kept simple as well.

103
00:05:41,590 --> 00:05:42,150
General.

104
00:05:43,210 --> 00:05:44,750
The proper rituals cannot be omitted.

105
00:05:45,210 --> 00:05:46,510
The General has mobility difficulties.

106
00:05:46,570 --> 00:05:47,750
I regret to say
that he can't complete the three bows.

107
00:05:48,110 --> 00:05:49,330
Since you've
already entered the residence,

108
00:05:49,790 --> 00:05:50,770
let's consider the ceremony completed.

109
00:06:07,650 --> 00:06:09,830
I never expected
the esteemed Northern General

110
00:06:09,910 --> 00:06:11,070
to be so nonchalant.

111
00:06:11,210 --> 00:06:14,050
Are you looking down on
the marriage bestowed by His Majesty?

112
00:06:14,150 --> 00:06:16,250
I simply look down on you.

113
00:06:18,410 --> 00:06:19,690
That suits me just fine.

114
00:06:19,990 --> 00:06:20,910
It's exactly what I want.

115
00:06:21,510 --> 00:06:22,850
However,
imperial orders can't be defied.

116
00:06:25,290 --> 00:06:27,330
If you drink this wine, General,

117
00:06:32,210 --> 00:06:33,210
we can consider the ceremony completed.

118
00:06:37,730 --> 00:06:39,150
You can drink it yourself.

119
00:06:41,770 --> 00:06:42,410
I won't drink it.

120
00:06:44,090 --> 00:06:45,490
I have no interest

121
00:06:45,530 --> 00:06:47,270
in wasting time here with you.

122
00:06:48,110 --> 00:06:48,870
Wait a moment.

123
00:07:29,110 --> 00:07:33,170
♪Fine rain infiltrates
the deep night, awakening the jasmine♪

124
00:07:35,010 --> 00:07:37,010
♪Two swallows build nests on the beam♪

125
00:07:37,270 --> 00:07:39,250
♪Carrying fresh mud in their beaks♪

126
00:07:41,330 --> 00:07:45,670
♪Gazing into the distance,
the path is filled with thriving grass♪

127
00:07:47,310 --> 00:07:51,910
♪The beautiful scene
feels undeserved by you♪

128
00:07:53,530 --> 00:07:55,410
♪The night wind suddenly rises♪

129
00:07:55,850 --> 00:07:58,050
♪Ruffling the rippling pool water♪

130
00:07:59,670 --> 00:08:03,650
♪The full moon is what I fear the most♪

131
00:08:04,770 --> 00:08:06,050
♪Similar smiles♪

132
00:08:06,130 --> 00:08:10,710
♪Conceal varying degrees of familiarity♪

133
00:08:11,410 --> 00:08:15,750
♪Emotions overflow
deeply; how much do you know♪

134
00:08:15,750 --> 00:08:18,650
♪I offer you a branch of jasmine♪

135
00:08:18,830 --> 00:08:21,850
♪May you never leave;
we rely on each other from dawn to dusk♪

136
00:08:22,290 --> 00:08:24,390
♪How easily we part, unbeknownst to us♪

137
00:08:24,850 --> 00:08:28,210
♪When we meet, there is
no predetermined time to return♪

